org.cpsolver.exam.model

Class PredefinedExamRoomSharing

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.exam.model.ExamRoomSharing
      • org.cpsolver.exam.model.PredefinedExamRoomSharing

  • public class PredefinedExamRoomSharing
extends ExamRoomSharing
    Room sharing model based on a pre-defined list of examination pairs. The relation needs to be populated using addPair(Exam, Exam) and it is persisted with the solution XML (see ExamModel.save(Assignment), canShareRoom element for each exam containing a comma separated list of exam ids).
    Version:
    ExamTT 1.3 (Examination Timetabling)
